You can create a request by entering the URL below.
Once this process is complete you will be shown the Headers and Body of the HTTP request you created. You can then send that request to the server.

data.name: textBox4.Text
data.value:
The Manual Testing section can contain multiple requests and so naming requests makes it easy to identify them.
When you click 'Create Request' you will be shown the HTTP Headers and Body of the request you created in previous section. You can edit it further or send it to the server and observe the response.
